OL,6,FA woman who was sexually assaulted
OL,7,Foutside her own front door by a man
OL,8,Fwho followed her home in Surrey says
OL,9,Fit has left her constantly afraid.
OL,11,FThe victim was walking home from
OL,12,FRedhill town centre on 4 August last
OL,13,Fyear when she noticed a man she didn't
OL,14,Fknow following close behind her.
OL,16,FAs she reached her front door and
OL,17,Ftried to get in, he grabbed her around
OL,18,Fthe neck and sexually assaulted her.
OL,19,FHe then exposed himself.
