OL,6,FThe woman was able to break free, but
OL,7,Fas she sought help, he continued to
OL,8,Ffollow her.
OL,10,FThe victim tried to flag down passing
OL,11,Fvehicles before spotting a neighbour
OL,12,Fwith their lights on, so she banged on
OL,13,Ftheir front door, they let her in and
OL,14,Fcalled the police.
OL,16,FOfficers found Deane Clayton, 37, from
OL,17,FNorthgate in Crawley, at Redhill bus
OL,18,Fstation where he was arrested.
